SCHEMA OF THE PIZZA SALES

Database
    ---pizzahut

Tables:
 1. pizzas
    --columns:
      ---pizza_id
      ---pizza_type_id
      ---size
      ---price
 2. pizza_types
    --columns:
      ---pizza_type_id
      ---name
      ---category
      ---ingredients
 3. orders
    --columns:
      ---order_id
      ---order_date
      ---order_time
 4. order_details
    --columns:
      ---order_details_id
      ---order_id
      ---pizza_id
      ---quantity
